<main>

<div class="hero" style="padding:72px 0 60px">
  <div class="wrap hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">01 · Visa Services</span>
    <h1>越南签证代办——十拿十稳</h1>
    <p class="lead">商务签、旅游签、长期签，皆由本地团队亲自送件与追踪，避免资料错误导致入境延误。成功率99.9%，比「十拿九稳」还多那么一点。</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">2–3天</div><div class="label">一般件平均出签时效</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">1天</div><div class="label">急件最快完成（需另计加急费用）</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">99.9%</div><div class="label">办理成功率</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="process">
      <div class="process-step"><span class="n">1</span><h4>上车</h4><p>告知目的、天数与行程，确认适用签证类型</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="n">2</span><h4>加满油</h4><p>提供材料清单，协助检查避免缺漏或错误</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="n">3</span><h4>开上路</h4><p>团队亲自送件并全程追踪进度</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="n">4</span><h4>抵达终点</h4><p>签证完成后主动通知，说明入境注意事项</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">签证类型对比</span>
      <h2>该办哪一种？</h2>
    </div>
    <table class="compare">
      <thead><tr><th>类型</th><th>适用情境</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>商务签</td><td>考察、洽谈、拜访合作对象，通常需邀请函或商务证明</td></tr>
        <tr><td>旅游签</td><td>一般观光、短期停留，申请条件相对简单</td></tr>
        <tr><td>长期签</td><td>长期居留、工作或多次进出需求</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;margin-top:20px">不确定自己适用哪一种？直接告诉我们你的目的与天数，团队会协助判断最适合的签证类型。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== 详细价目表 ===== -->
<section id="price-list">
